Perintah untuk mount hardisk/ssd di ubuntu
mengatasi hardisk format NTFS tidak bisa menulis

(base) wanwanvm@miswan-os:~$ sudo ntfsfix /dev/sdb1
[sudo] password for wanwanvm: 
Mounting volume... OK
Processing of $MFT and $MFTMirr completed successfully.
Checking the alternate boot sector... OK
NTFS volume version is 3.1.
NTFS partition /dev/sdb1 was processed successfully.
(base) wanwanvm@miswan-os:~$ sudo mount /dev/sdb1 /media/wanwanvm/

